title: Fleetway Sonic the Comic's (STC)
description:
There is another torrent claiming to have this but there&#039;s been no seeds forever now, so I&#039;m re-adding it.

The files are in .cbr (CDisplay RAR Archived Comic Book File) format, which is basically a bunch of pics in a rar file with a different extention.  I&#039;ve included the program recommended for viewing them, or if you prefer you can just use winrar to extract the jpeg&#039;s.

This torrent has every official fleetway Sonic the Comic, including the specials, an advert for the comic, the yearbooks and the poster mags.

Enjoy all!
